INSERT INTO `cms_page_versions` VALUES (36,13,'en','Home','<p>Homepage</p>','1','2012-02-27 23:52:46','2012-02-27 23:52:46','2012-02-27 23:52:46'),(37,14,'en','At Risk: Education IT','<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">At-Risk Education IT </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you are the person responsible for the computers and IT at your school, we&rsquo;re willing to bet that you&rsquo;re concerned about cost, security, a stress-free experience, and more. It could be you are here because you need help with an existing system. Maybe you know it&rsquo;s time to put in a new network. Or it could be a combination of both. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">You&rsquo;ve come to the right place. Not only are we the premier choice for your IT needs, we have the specific experience needed to understand your school&rsquo;s best interests. Our work with the Boys Republic of Chino, Somerset Educational Services, and other local boarding schools has given us the edge needed to serve you. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Security and privacy </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">You\'re likely aware how important is to protect the personal information of students enrolled<br /> at your institution. We\'re right there with you on that. Work with our experts to lock down<br /> your records with ABSS NetSecure. We do it with sophisticated hardware firewalls that keep malicious content from getting in or out. We do it with patch management on every component in your network. We do it with vulnerability testing and assessment conducted by our experts. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Migrate to Mac computer networks </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Apple has long been at the forefront when it comes to computerizing education. If you\'re looking to replace part or all of your Windows-based network with machines that run the Mac OS, you\'re in the right place. Talk to us about network design. Have us assemble a configuration that does exactly what you want it to do. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Integrate Mac and Windows machines into one efficient network </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If administration is running fine on Windows-based PCs and the teachers and students are working away in a separate Mac network, you may think it best to leave well enough alone. The thing is, when you stay this course, you lose efficiency and the ability to communicate with classrooms and monitor their activity. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Integrate your networks with help from ABSS. While we\'re there, we can put content filtering in place. Read on to learn more. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Internet content filtering </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Keep students and instructors on task by removing distractions online. The amount of time people spend looking at social and pornographic websites is staggering. We\'re willing to bet you have Facebook open in another window or tab right now. Don\'t be surprised if we\'re right. One of every twelve people on the planet has a Facebook account. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Eliminate the tremendous temptation to see what friends are saying and protect your organization from legal action with content filtering. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data backup and restoration </span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Work with us to save every bit of student record data you can. Our custom onsite and globally accessible offsite backup with DataVault are designed with your specific needs in mind. Data restoration is easy and secure at the same time. As long as you have internet access and your security key, your restoration can be initiated any time. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Solutions </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We solve problems that stem from trying to get by with part-time support or self help. We define the right way to protect your systems, connect your networks, and manage your data. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call today. It\'s the smart thing to do. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks: 866-479-6200&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-02-28 18:50:09','2012-02-28 18:50:09','2012-02-28 18:50:09'),(38,15,'en','Nine Reasons for ABSS Computer Networks','<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Nine reasons your business should use ABSS Computer Networks In-Sourced IT </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">It&rsquo;s likely that there are more than 2,832,371 reasons to use In-Sourced IT. Most of them relate to the nine listed here. If even one of these applies to you, please contact us today. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">You are not in the business of IT. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ Look at it this way: If your company designs and builds, say, digital cameras, it&rsquo;s unlikely your employees would get involved in replacing the plumbing in your building. You might have a person or two that&rsquo;s handy with a wrench and torch, but in the grand scheme of things, those people are more valuable when they are doing what they were hired to do. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">The same scenario applies to your office network. Your camera people may be technologically inclined, but they are probably best suited to developing new CCDs rather than programming firewalls. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Our business is taking care of your network. Put us to work. â—‹ </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">In-house professionals are expensive </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">â—‹ Full time IT experts are worth their weight in gold. Yes. We are sounding our own horn here, but we believe in what we do. We give you our best. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">The thing is, even if you are experiencing major network problems, you probably do not need one of us in your office every hour of every day. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Your solution is to sign with ABSS for In-Sourced and Managed IT. You&rsquo;ll get all the kno