al\';\">The Federal Reserve Board spells things out with clarity: &ldquo;...a financial institution should review the structure of its computer network to determine how its computers are accessible from outside the institution. If the computer systems are connected to the Internet or any outside party, an institution&rsquo;s assessment should address the reasonably foreseeable threats posed by that connectivity.&rdquo; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We follow regulatory guidelines. It&rsquo;s as simple as that. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Compliance </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Count on us to stay up-to-date with the NCUA&rsquo;s Information Service and Technology (IS&amp;T) Examination Program. We review your union&rsquo;s computer networking systems with intense focus on audit, information technology, member services, and security. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data protection </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Trust us to take security seriously. We do it with sophisticated hardware firewalls that keep malicious content from getting in or out. We do it with patch management on every component in your network. We do it with vulnerability testing and assessment conducted by our ABSS NetSecure experts. They test to eliminate external, internal, and dormant threats. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data backup and restoration </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Work with us to save every bit of financial data you can. Our custom onsite and global offsite backup with DataVault are designed with your specific needs in mind. Data restoration is easy and secure at the same time. As long as you have internet access and your security key, your restoration can be initiated any time. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Solutions </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We solve problems that stem from trying to get by with part-time support or self help. We define the right way to protect your systems and manage your data. We are there in the evenings or on weekends because your financial clients expect access and service every day at any moment. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call today. It makes practical and financial sense </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks: &lt;cms:var id=\"phone\" /&gt;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-02-28 19:15:43','2012-02-28 19:15:43','2012-02-28 19:15:43'),(55,26,'en','About ABSS Computer Networks','<p>About Content Here</p>','1','2012-02-28 19:24:59','2012-02-28 19:24:59','2012-02-28 19:24:59'),(56,27,'en','Contact','<p>Contact ABSS Computer Networks</p>','1','2012-02-28 19:26:08','2012-02-28 19:26:08','2012-02-28 19:26:08'),(57,28,'en','Services','<h1>Services Provided by ABSS Networks, Inc.</h1>','1','2012-02-28 19:26:55','2012-02-28 19:26:55','2012-02-28 19:26:55'),(58,20,'en','Managed IT','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\">Managed IT</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All the network services you need organized into levels that fit your business. Choose the one that works for you. All of them include the following: </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Network Monitoring with ABSS ClearView </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you&rsquo;ve ever looked at a rack of servers (or even just stood next to a desktop computer), you&rsquo;ve likely noticed how difficult it is to tell that, say, a critical hard drive is on its last legs. After all, if it isn&rsquo;t making crunchy grinding noises, it&rsquo;s &ldquo;likely&rdquo; doing just fine. Banking on &ldquo;likely&rdquo; is similar to rolling the dice. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you could see inside, things might look a little clearer (and you won&rsquo;t have to gamble). </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Our ClearView monitoring lets us do exactly that. It&rsquo;s a window to the inner workings of your network. With it we can: </span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Communicate with a secure, invisible connection</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All transmissions to and from your network are encrypted via SSL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">The monitoring agent uses almost no system resources. You will not see any&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">network slow-downs.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Manage and monitor Servers, Networks and Workstations</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Choose the plan that&rsquo;s right for you. We can cover one server or an entire network</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Find problems before they happen</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">ClearView checks the operation of your equipment against known baselines.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Hardware failure is usually preceded by small changes in operation. We get&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">notified the instant that happens.</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Fix many problems without coming in</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">ClearView and our Managed IT service includes remote repair when possible. Most remote services don&rsquo;t need a person on your end at all.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Keep antivirus up-to-date on all your machines</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">It&rsquo;s not likely that all your employees think to maintain their own machines. Some&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">might. We make sure all computers are protected.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Keep everything patched</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">P</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">rogram updates are regular events. It&rsquo;s hard enough to keep track when you use two programs on three machines. Many of our customers have tens of programs on hundreds of computers. We update them all.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Track the inventory and age of your hardware</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\"><br /></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">We catalog the hardware in each machine. If something needs to be replaced,</span></li>\r\n<li>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">we&rsquo;ll know what it is without interrupting your day. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;You are informed when equipment is going out of warranty. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Maintain software license agreements </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Program installations are tracked. If you get close to exceeding allotted seats, we </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">will let you know. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;We&rsquo;ll track illegal software downloads. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Generate a report </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ Since our monitoring is mostly invisible, we document our activity and supply it in a monthly, easy-to-read report. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call the Help Desk </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Sometimes all you want is an e-mail account for a new salesperson. This is the sort of thing we handle in minutes. All you need to do is request it. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Maybe an employee forgot a password and entered the wrong one too many times. They&rsquo;re locked out of their own machine and can not get any work done. We can resolve this during office hours with one quick phone call. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All our levels of service include some amount of this kind of help. We&rsquo;re like that tech-savvy friend that so many people have. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Come to think of it, we&rsquo;re also a friend of that friend. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">We&rsquo;re the Expert&rsquo;s Expert when you need one </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Here&rsquo;s where things get interesting (or complicated, if you&rsquo;re not a computer person at heart). Could be you have a flat ethernet network with 524 end-users and a few server farms. The network performance is poor from time to time and you&rsquo;re not sure what to do next. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">You&rsquo;ve asked your in-house IT to do analysis and possibly redesign the current infrastructure to improve performance. Your employee is top-notch and usually takes any problem and<br /> just handles it. This time, however, the initial response to your request was an expression of excitement that slowly degenerated into abject terror. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Your IT experts have not kept up with technology. They&rsquo;re not sure what to do next, either. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Of course this scenario is quite a bit better than having an under-qualified, over-confident staff member just diving in and hoping they can swim. It takes training, experience, and life-long learning to avoid drowning in an ocean of routers, cables, switches, and CPUs. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">This is another reason we&rsquo;re here &ndash; to be your IT expert&rsquo;s expert. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Maybe your network slow-down problem stems from too many data collisions. It&rsquo;s possible that segmentation is the answer. We need to start by taking a look inside. The best thing to do right now is call us at ###-###-#### to find out for sure. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Levels of Service </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Platinum Support: </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Weekly Network Server Health Check, Analysis &amp; Reporting </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Microsoft Service Pack &amp; Security Patch Notifications </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Unlimited Remote Voice &amp; Remote Support </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Best Effort Emergency Onsite Response </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Reduced onsite service rates </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;No Charge Portal to Portal Travel </sp