l (per quote) </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;No Premium for Emergency \"Demand now\" Services </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Monthly Support Usage Reporting </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Bronze Support: </span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Weekly Network Server Health Check, Analysis &amp; Reporting </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Microsoft Service Pack &amp; Security Patch Notifications </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Limited Remote Voice &amp; Remote Support </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Best Effort Emergency Onsite Response </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Standard ABSS onsite service rates apply </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;No Premium for Emergency \"Demand now\" Services </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">&acirc;ï¿½ï¿½ &nbsp;Monthly Support Usage Reporting&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-02-28 19:29:50','2012-02-28 19:29:50','2012-02-28 19:29:50'),(59,14,'en','Education IT','<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">At-Risk Education IT </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you are the person responsible for the computers and IT at your school, we&rsquo;re willing to bet that you&rsquo;re concerned about cost, security, a stress-free experience, and more. It could be you are here because you need help with an existing system. Maybe you know it&rsquo;s time to put in a new network. Or it could be a combination of both. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">You&rsquo;ve come to the right place. Not only are we the premier choice for your IT needs, we have the specific experience needed to understand your school&rsquo;s best interests. Our work with the Boys Republic of Chino, Somerset Educational Services, and other local boarding schools has given us the edge needed to serve you. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Security and privacy </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">You\'re likely aware how important is to protect the personal information of students enrolled&nbsp;at your institution. We\'re right there with you on that. Work with our experts to lock down&nbsp;your records with ABSS NetSecure. We do it with sophisticated hardware firewalls that keep malicious content from getting in or out. We do it with patch management on every component in your network. We do it with vulnerability testing and assessment conducted by our experts. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Migrate to Mac computer networks </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Apple has long been at the forefront when it comes to computerizing education. If you\'re looking to replace part or all of your Windows-based network with machines that run the Mac OS, you\'re in the right place. Talk to us about network design. Have us assemble a configuration that does exactly what you want it to do. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Integrate Mac and Windows machines into one efficient network </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If administration is running fine on Windows-based PCs and the teachers and students are working away in a separate Mac network, you may think it best to leave well enough alone. The thing is, when you stay this course, you lose efficiency and the ability to communicate with classrooms and monitor their activity. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Integrate your networks with help from ABSS. While we\'re there, we can put content filtering in place. Read on to learn more. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Internet content filtering </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Keep students and instructors on task by removing distractions online. The amount of time people spend looking at social and pornographic websites is staggering. We\'re willing to bet you have Facebook open in another window or tab right now. Don\'t be surprised if we\'re right. One of every twelve people on the planet has a Facebook account. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Eliminate the tremendous temptation to see what friends are saying and protect your organization from legal action with content filtering. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data backup and restoration</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Work wi