\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;\">ABSS - In-Sourced IT</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">In-Sourced IT from ABSS - It&rsquo;s like adding a team of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\">computer professionals to your staff without having to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\">make room for extra desks</span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Since you&rsquo;re reading this, we&rsquo;re willing to bet that you&rsquo;re experiencing some kind of problem with your business computers. It could be anything from an error message that pops up randomly to hours of lost time due to outdated hardware and software. The real issue is that you don&rsquo;t have a solution, the time required to find one, or a person on staff that can do it for you. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">This is exactly why you should call us: We have your solution. We have your person. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">It&rsquo;s also possible you or your IT people are great with computers. You often know the solution to the problems that pop up. But as time marches on, you and your staff just don&rsquo;t have enough space in the schedule to keep up with new technology. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">This is also exactly why you should call us: We are the expert&rsquo;s expert when it comes to computer networks. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">What we&rsquo;re offering you is In-Sourced IT. You get the professional help you need without having to