11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We&rsquo;re not talking about a person who doesn&rsquo;t want to work. This is about employees that care about the company and do their best. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Every so often, even your most dedicated people will bite off more than they can chew. They may think, as they do with their other responsibilities, that maintaining the network will be a rewarding challenge. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">The trouble arises when the challenge goes beyond their abilities. It takes uncommon mental fortitude to swallow and digest the difficult problems. It&rsquo;s not that your person lacks the hunger. It&rsquo;s just that they&rsquo;re not prepared to consume IT work in the same portions as the job for which they were hired. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Feed us your IT work. We really eat it up..</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Your IT person is overloaded </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Give that person some help from ABSS. They&rsquo;re into what they do and they are great at it. Your employee lacks only the time needed to get everything done. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If It&rsquo;s not time to add a second professional to your staff, the welcomed assistance can come from our In-Sourced IT service. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Technology has advanced beyond the skills of your IT person </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Keep your network up-to-date with technology and keep your expert professional on staff. Bring ABSS Computer Networks in as your expert&rsquo;s expert. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">It&rsquo;s only natural that as technology marches on, dedicated employees with a full plate of work can have trouble keeping up. There is likely not enough time in the day for them to train and learn. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Don&rsquo;t forget that network problems with elusive solutions have a tendency to materialize without warning or reason. For those extra-challenging ones, a second expert can often make for a quicker victory in the ever-lasting battle to maintain a perfect network. Give your IT person the help they need (but only when it&rsquo;s needed) by signing up with ABSS today. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">It&rsquo;s hard to find the IT person you actually need </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Here&rsquo;s a tough spot: you&rsquo;re having network problems, you think you need a professional on staff, and, since you are not an IT expert yourself, you do not have a clear idea about which person to hire. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Put ABSS on the job. We&rsquo;ll take care of your computer problems now and help you determine if a full time expert on staff is right for you. We realize that we might be limiting our future involvement with that kind of advice, but our goal is your satisfaction and the peace of mind that only an efficient and smooth-running network can bring. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 12.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">You are often bringing in a consultant </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Understand that we appreciate loyalty in our field. If