ze: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Trust us to take security seriously. We use advanced hardware firewalls to prevent malicious content from getting in or out. We apply patch management across every piece of equipment in your network. Our ABSS NetSecure experts conduct vulnerability testing and assessment to minimize external and internal threats - even if they&rsquo;re dormant. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data backup and restoration </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Work with us to save every bit of medical data you can. Our network specific onsite backup<br /> and world-wide offsite backup with DataVault are designed with your specific needs in mind. Restoration is simultaneously secure and easy. If you have your unique security key and access to the internet, you can initiate file restoration at any time. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Solutions </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We solve problems that stem from trying to maintain your network with part-time support or<br /> self help. We understand the correct way to manage medical data. and protect the integrity of your systems. We are active in the evenings and on weekends because your doctors, staff, and patients need to have access and service every day at any moment. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call us today </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks: ###-###-####&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-03-21 22:56:08','2012-03-21 22:56:08','2012-03-21 22:56:08'),(111,16,'en','Credit Unions','<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\">Credit Unions</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you control a new institution or one that&rsquo;s looking to expand, you know the rules and restrictions imposed upon you. When it comes to your technology, go with an In-sourced IT company that understands how you must operate. Go with ABSS Computer Networks. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Regulations </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">The Federal Reserve Board spells things out with clarity: &ldquo;...a financial institution should review the structure of its computer network to determine how its computers are accessible from outside the institution. If the computer systems are connected to the Internet or any outside party, an institution&rsquo;s assessment should address the reasonably foreseeable threats posed by that connectivity.&rdquo; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We follow regulatory guidelines. It&rsquo;s as simple as that. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Compliance </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Count on us to stay up-to-date with the NCUA&rsquo;s Information Service and Technology (IS&amp;T) Examination Program. We review your union&rsquo;s computer networking systems with intense focus on audit, information technology, member services, and security. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data protection </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Trust us to take security seriously. We do it with sophisticated hardware firewalls that keep malicious content from getting in or out. We do it with patch management on every component in your network. We do it with vulnerability testing and assessment conducted by our ABSS NetSecure experts. They test to eliminate external, internal, and dormant threats. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data backup and restoration </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Work with us to save every bit of financial data you can. Our custom onsite and global offsite backup with DataVault are designed with your specific needs in mind. Data restoration is easy and secure at the same time. As long as you have internet access and your security key, your restoration can be initiated any time. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Solutions </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We solve problems that stem from trying to get by with part-time support or self help. We define the right way to protect your systems and manage your data. We are there in the evenings or on weekends because your financial clients expect access and service every day at any moment. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call today. It makes practical and financial sense </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks: &lt;cms:var id=\"phone\" /&gt;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-03-21 22:56:17','2012-03-21 22:56:17','2012-03-21 22:56:17'),(112,29,'en','Our Brands','<h1>Our Brands</h1>\r\n<p>ABSS Inc. provides the highest level of quality with brand names that you can trust.</p>','1','2012-03-21 22:57:51','2012-03-21 22:57:51','2012-03-21 22:57:51'),(113,21,'en','Network Design by ABSS','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"float: right; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"../../../../app/assets/images/sitting-laptop.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" />Network Design by ABSS Networks, Inc.</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Since you are reading this, we&rsquo;re willing to bet your business is expanding and it&rsquo;s time to build a new computer network. It&rsquo;s an advantageous position for sure. You&rsquo;ve increased your income and can now increase your efficiency to match. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Eliminate your troubles when it comes to finding the best network design for your company. If you&rsquo;re in the business of Education, Healthcare, Finance, (or anything else, really), there&rsquo;s no reason </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-style: italic;\">you </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">need to decide on using Bus, Ring, Tree, Star, or Mesh Topology. Leave that decision, and others like it, to the experts at ABSS. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Talk to us about a network that&rsquo;s sized right and does exactly what it&rsquo;s supposed to do. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Scalable Networks </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Large-sized, small-sized, and, well, let&rsquo;s just call them &ldquo;all-sized&rdquo; - we&rsquo;ll create one that works for your company today, tomorrow, and years from now. Take advantage of this fresh start with a network that can grow and shrink with your needs. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Order a scalable system from ABSS. Then, when it&rsquo;s time to add a machine for one person or twenty three for an entire team, the expansion can often take place in a day or less. The same goes for contractions (like the sale of a successful business unit). Your sold equipment can be quickly disconnected without compromising network function and integrity. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Call today. We&rsquo;ll meet with you and discuss what you want to get done. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Routers, switches, modems, and more </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">The number of components that make a fully functioning network can boggle the mind. It gets worse once you discover how many of them need to be connected, configured, and, for lack of a better term, convinced to do their job. Make things better for yourself by letting us cover the details. It&rsquo;s what we&rsquo;re good at. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Wireless networking </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Opening your network to the air can be a convenience dream and security nightmare all at the same time. It&rsquo;s easy to sleep blissfully knowing that a new computer can see the network from anywhere in your building. It&rsquo;s also easy to get jarred awake by the thought of someone parking outside and breaking in with a laptop. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Put your concerns to bed with wireless network design by ABSS Computer Networks. We&rsquo;ll cover the basics (like putting the access point in a place where all devices can see it) and the specifics (like making sure that your settings are configured to keep unwanted users out). </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Server recommendation, configuration, and installation </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Trust us to suggest a machine that&rsquo;s more than enough to do the job and yet not excessive. Maybe one computer is enough. Maybe you&rsquo;ll need a group of them to balance the load. Maybe </span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">you could benefit from virtual machines. No matter what, we&rsquo;ll look at your goal and build, configure, and install a server (or servers) that will accomplish it. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Workstation recommendation, configuration, and installation </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We&rsquo;ll take into account what you and your employees will do at your desks and specify machines that fit your demands. It&rsquo;s likely those machines won&rsquo;t be one-size-fits-all. We&rsquo;ll use our expertise to build workstations that can do just a bit more than they&rsquo;re supposed to. That way you won&rsquo;t need to upgrade quite so soon. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Configure and install network printers </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Most days it&rsquo;s easy to print. Just put what you want on the screen, and, well, select print. If you&rsquo;ve ever tried to add a printer and make it visible to everyone, you might already understand why we offer this service. If there was ever one type of device that hates to play nice, this would be it. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Onsite data backup and recovery </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Now that we&rsquo;ve got a network for your data to move about, let us help keep you from losing it. We can configure onsite data storage and automatic backup. Rest assured that if a hard drive fails in spectacular fashion or someone accidentally deletes a file with a whimper, you&rsquo;ll be able to retrieve your latest backup in minutes. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Remember that even the best onsite systems can&rsquo;t protect data from disaster. Fires, floods and earthquakes don&rsquo;t seem to discriminate when it comes to destruction of property. Look into our offsite backup service to protect your most sensitive data in secure locations around the globe. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Point-of-failure elimination with redundancy </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Seems like no matter what you do, something just breaks without warning. Maybe a power supply gets tired and pops or a hard drive just kinda wheezes and clunks to a halt. Usually our network monitoring service spots an anomaly before it turns into a failure. But every once in a while a machine will just give up the ghost without so much as flicker of notice. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks are designed with redundancy in mind. If a critical portion of the network stops working, other machines step in to take up the slack.You&rsquo;ll likely feel it in the form of a slow-down here or there, but our monitoring will tell us immediately that something is up (or down as the case may be).<br /> If you&rsquo;ve signed up for Managed IT, we&rsquo;ll know what to bring before you even call for service. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Call today and get a new network </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">ABSS Computer Networks: ###-###-####&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"section\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-03-21 22:59:50','2012-03-21 22:59:50','2012-03-21 22:59:50'),(114,28,'en','Services Provided','<h1>Services Provided by ABSS Networks, Inc.</h1>','1','2012-03-21 23:01:01','2012-03-21 23:01:01','2012-03-21 23:01:01'),(115,24,'en','Disaster & Recovery Planning','<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"float: right; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"../../../../app/assets/images/remove-server.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" />Disaster &amp; Recovery Planning</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Your data is the lifeblood of your business. If you lose too much of it, your company may die. We know this sounds harsh and maybe a little dramatic, but there are not many other ways to say it. Fortunately, we have an comparatively light-hearted solution: Data backup with DataVault by ABSS Computer Networks. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Some data loss can&rsquo;t be helped </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you&rsquo;ve ever accidentally deleted a file, it was exactly that - an accident. The same goes for dumping liquids into your computer. You have some control over this, but if you work long enough, these things just happen. Same goes for hard drive failure. It&rsquo;s something that can&rsquo;t be helped. After a while, they just give up. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Save all the data you can </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">First off, make sure you have local, onsite backups. If you need help setting this up, let us know. Every workstation and server that sees action on a daily basis should be backed-up every day (or even every hour if the work load is heavy). There&rsquo;s nothing quite like the relief that comes from retrieving a file that was accidentally erased two hours before (especially if that file took three hours to make). </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Back up the most important data safely and securely </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">When it comes to critical information, even the best onsite backups can not protect you<br /> from things like theft, fire, or floods. Store your sensitive data in a vault - a DataVault from ABSS. They&rsquo;re located around the world. This means we keep backups of your backups. Our encryption is military grade - you are the only one who can access your data. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Restore data from anywhere at any time </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-siz