07:24','2012-03-21 23:07:24','2012-03-21 23:07:24'),(122,19,'en','In-Sourced IT','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"float: right; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"../../../../app/assets/images/post-its.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" />ABSS - In-Sourced IT</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">In-Sourced IT from ABSS - It&rsquo;s like adding a team of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\">computer professionals to your staff without having to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\">make room for extra desks</span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Since you&rsquo;re reading this, we&rsquo;re willing to bet that you&rsquo;re experiencing some kind of problem with your business computers. It could be anything from an error message that pops up randomly to hours of lost time due to outdated hardware and software. The real issue is that you don&rsquo;t have a solution, the time required to find one, or a person on staff that can do it for you. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">This is exactly why you should call us: We have your solution. We have your person. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">It&rsquo;s also possible you or your IT people are great with computers. You often know the solution to the problems that pop up. But as time marches on, you and your staff just don&rsquo;t have enough space in the schedule to keep up with new technology. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">This is also exactly why you should call us: We are the expert&rsquo;s expert when it comes to computer networks. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">What we&rsquo;re offering you is In-Sourced IT. You get the professional help you need without having to make more room in your office. You don&rsquo;t need to call across the globe for assistance. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We&rsquo;re local to Riverside, California. We can also provide some of our services to the entire United States. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Talk to us about Managed IT. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We provide field services, like on-site repair, to customers within 51 miles of us. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Maybe you need off-site data storage. We do that, too. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Have us filter your e-mail for spam. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We can secure your network or help you design a new one. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">We&rsquo;ve got years of experience with general business and specific types of customers. If you manage a Credit Union or a Local Health Care facility, please call us today. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you&rsquo;re in charge of a Non-Profit or a school for at-risk students, we&rsquo;ve got a program that works for you. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Call ABSS Computer Networks at &lt;cms:phone /&gt; for the solutions and services you need.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','1','2012-03-21 23:07:33','2012-03-21 23:07:33','2012-03-21 23:07:33'),(123,20,'en','Managed & Field IT Services','<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"float: right; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;\" src=\"../../../../app/assets/images/man-rack.jpg\" alt=\"\" />Managed &amp; Field IT Services</span></h1>\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All the network services you need organized into levels that fit your business. Choose the one that works for you. All of them include the following: </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Network Monitoring with ABSS ClearView </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you&rsquo;ve ever looked at a rack of servers (or even just stood next to a desktop computer), you&rsquo;ve likely noticed how difficult it is to tell that, say, a critical hard drive is on its last legs. After all, if it isn&rsquo;t making crunchy grinding noises, it&rsquo;s &ldquo;likely&rdquo; doing just fine. Banking on &ldquo;likely&rdquo; is similar to rolling the dice. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">If you could see inside, things might look a little clearer (and you won&rsquo;t have to gamble). </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Our ClearView monitoring lets us do exactly that. It&rsquo;s a window to the inner workings of your network. With it we can: </span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Communicate with a secure, invisible connection</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">All transmissions to and from your network are encrypted via SSL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">The monitoring agent uses almost no system resources. You will not see any&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">network slow-downs.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Manage and monitor Servers, Networks and Workstations</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Choose the plan that&rsquo;s right for you. We can cover one server or an entire network</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Find problems before they happen</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">ClearView checks the operation of your equipment against known baselines.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Hardware failure is usually preceded by small changes in operation. We get&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">notified the instant that happens.</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Fix many problems without coming in</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">ClearView and our Managed IT service includes remote repair when possible. Most remote services don&rsquo;t need a person on your end at all.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Keep antivirus up-to-date on all your machines</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">It&rsquo;s not likely that all your employees think to maintain their own machines. Some&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">might. We make sure all computers are protected.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Keep everything patched</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">P</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">rogram updates are regular events. It&rsquo;s hard enough to keep track when you use two programs on t