 your income stream with one call to ABSS Computer Networks at &lt;cms:phone /&gt;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Computer hardware repair </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Sometimes parts just give up. Hard drives stop spinning. Power supplies let the smoke out. RAM loses its memory. These things happen. When the machines break, call us and we will come fix them. It&rsquo;s easy. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Make it even easier by signing up for Managed IT. We&rsquo;re usually warned ahead of time is something is about to give up by our ClearView Network Monitoring service. If you request a repair, we&rsquo;ll have the right parts with us when we arrive at your doorstep. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Computer software problems </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Pop-ups and warnings are the wrong ways to start the day. If you or your employees are experiencing these on a regular basis, they are cutting into time best spent on getting things done. You could be seeing signs of malware, spyware, viruses, missing files, or just run-of-the- mill registry issues that manifest for seemingly no reason at all. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Call us today to knock out the pop-ups, answer the warnings, and make your next day start off right (or, at least, free of pop-ups and warnings). </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Expanding your network </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Increasing business and adding employees goes hand-in-hand with installing more machines. It&rsquo;s not likely that you can just plug a computer into your switch and get everything to mesh automatically. Network settings need to be configured. You&rsquo;ll probably need a few software installs. Have us take care of that for you. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Maybe you&rsquo;ve acquired another company and want to connect your networks. Talk to us about security and setting up a VPN. If you need a completely new network design, we can do that, too. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">Data Migration </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Transfer important files from old servers and workstations to your new machines with data migration services from ABSS Computer Networks. </span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\'; font-weight: bold;\">More onsite services </span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Choose us for any of your onsite needs involving computer networking, hardware, and software.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\r\n<div class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\r\n<div class=\"column\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Here&rsquo;s a list of more services we offer. </span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">Data Backup &amp; Recovery</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 11.000000pt; font-family: \'Arial\';\">D</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">esktop &amp; Laptop Repair</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Firewall Installation</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">General Maintenance</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt;\">Hard Drive Recovery</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-s